<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Data Privacy Challenges</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <style>
    /* Reset and Base */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f7f9fc;
      color: #111119;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding-top: 80px;
    }

    /* Header/Navbar */
    header {
      background-color: purple;
      padding: 3rem;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
      gap: 1.8rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 0;
    }

    nav ul li a {
      color: #ecf0f1;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover,
    nav ul li a.active {
      background-color: #418dda;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .privacy-container {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 30px auto 50px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px 50px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 74, 173, 0.1);
    }

    .main-title {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #002766;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .challenges-section,
    .enforcement-section {
      margin-bottom: 45px;
    }

    .challenges-section h2,
    .enforcement-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #003a99;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #004aad;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .intro-text {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-style: italic;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .table-container {
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .challenges-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .challenges-table thead tr {
      background-color: #004aad;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .challenges-table th,
    .challenges-table td {
      padding: 15px 18px;
    }

    .challenges-table tbody tr {
      background: #f9fbff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .challenges-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
      background: #eaf0ff;
    }

    .challenges-table tbody tr:hover {
      background-color: #d1defd;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .enforcement-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .text-block h3 {
      color: #004aad;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .text-block p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: purple;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .privacy-container {
        padding: 25px 20px;
        margin: 20px 15px 40px;
      }

      .main-title {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      .challenges-table th,
      .challenges-table td {
        padding: 12px 10px;
      }

      nav ul {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.6rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      
      <%- include('partials/navbar', {currentPage: 'challenges'}) %>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="privacy-container">
    <h1 class="main-title">Data Privacy Challenges in the Digital Age</h1>

    <section class="challenges-section">
      <h2>What Are the Key Challenges for Individuals and Companies?</h2>
      <p class="intro-text">As reported by <em>(Bisht, 2024)</em>, here are some of the most significant data privacy challenges faced today:</p>

      <div class="table-container">
        <table class="challenges-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>#</th>
              <th>Challenge</th>
              <th>Description</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>1</td><td>Lack of Data Transparency</td><td>Apps collect personal data without clearly informing users about how it's used or shared.</td></tr>
            <tr><td>2</td><td>Risks of Cloud Computing</td><td>Cloud storage increases exposure to breaches, especially with weak security or foreign storage laws.</td></tr>
            <tr><td>3</td><td>Weak Data Protection Laws</td><td>Inconsistent or weak laws allow unchecked data collection and misuse.</td></tr>
            <tr><td>4</td><td>Frequent Data Breaches</td><td>Human error, hacking, or theft often exposes sensitive personal data.</td></tr>
            <tr><td>5</td><td>Excessive Data Retention</td><td>Holding onto data too long increases risks of leaks or unethical use.</td></tr>
            <tr><td>6</td><td>Emerging Technologies (AI/IoT)</td><td>AI and IoT collect large data volumes, risking misuse or unauthorized profiling.</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="enforcement-section">
      <h2>Challenges in Enforcing Data Privacy</h2>

      <div class="enforcement-content">
        <div class="text-block">
          <h3>Compliance and Implementation Difficulties</h3>
          <p>Despite strict regulations, compliance remains difficult—especially for small businesses—due to high costs and complexity <em>(Tankard, 2016)</em>. Multinational companies also face legal conflicts across jurisdictions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-block">
          <h3>Technical Limitations</h3>
          <p>Balancing data utility and privacy is challenging: heavy anonymization reduces research value <em>(Ohm, 2010)</em>, while de-anonymization attacks show even "secure" data can be re-identified <em>(Shmatikov, 2008)</em>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-block">
          <h3>Emerging Privacy Threats</h3>
          <p>AI and big data analytics can extract private details from seemingly anonymous datasets. IoT expands surveillance risks, increasing exposure to leaks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 Data Privacy Project</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
